      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. This car has been my pride and joy, and it seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously cared for\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for someone who truly appreciates a car in perfect, pristine condition. You've got to see it to believe how gorgeous it is!",
