    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered lineage. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a high-revving, linear power delivery. Mated to a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. Crucial preventative maintenance, including con-rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, has been meticulously performed. The factory suspension maintains its original damping characteristics, and the hydraulic steering rack offers uncompromised feedback. An analytically perfect specimen for the enthusiast who demands mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
