    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade vehicle that represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain or a flake of snow. The exterior paint is in showroom condition, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections of any kind. Every body panel is original with perfect alignment. Inside, the interior remains in 'as-new' state, with the leather upholstery still firm and supple, retaining its original factory scent. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the ambient lighting, operate with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the top side. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a virtually new vehicle that has been pampered by a single dedicated enthusiast. Inspections are welcomed and encouraged to verify the extraordinary condition of this machine.",
      "price": 44800.0,
